Figure 1a depicts our experimental platform consisting of a linear ion trap, along with a single ion. Figure 1b presents a schematic of the two-level working fluid (in the following also referred to as the engine), which is coupled to one of the ion’s vibrational modes, which is the load, shown in Fig. 1c. To represent the state of the atom, we use the basis states σ,n\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
